- All drapes are dead hung
- Proscenium Thickness is 8"
- Drapery Distances from Upstage Proscenium Wall - Measurements are from Centre of pipe and do not account for fullness of drapes


# Onstage - Show Power
-3ph 100amp disconnect located SL (electrician required for connection, no pigtails installed)
-Single ph 50 amp disconnect switch located SL, Stove Plug


# Lighting - Control System 
-ETC Ion XE 20 with fader wing
-2x Lenovo 17 inch touchscreen monitors

-House Lights - ETC ArcSystem LED Dimmable system
-15x Arcsystem Pro 1-Cell Recessed Fixtures - 3000k
-ETC Response N4g-DIN Gateway touch screen controller (Echo ETS)
-ArcMesh TX1 Wireless Transmitter 

# Lighting - Dimmers 
- ETC Sensor3 - 96 2.4k dimmers
- Power-Thru provided by Parked Addresses on Console


# Lighting - Circuits
All conventional fixtures and circuits are 20amp 120v twist-lok (L5-20)
 
